  "title": "BIM Coordinator",
  "description": "<p>Prepare 2D & 3D presentation/design drawings. \n• Using Building Information Modelling (BIM) to perform drawing works. \n• Coordinating submission schedules, monitor modelling/update drawing and \ninform key personnel if there are any changes. \n• Creating and updating BIM Models based on contract drawings and the latest \ninformation. \n• Preparing models for Clash Detection Coordination. \n• Working closely with the project team in coordination, organization and \npreparation of documents and drawings, adhering to BIM execution plan and BIM \nproject workflow criteria. \n• Other BIM-related duties that may be required to perform.</p>",
